    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 342660.0,
      "end_time": 345260.0,
      "text": "Some countries have large industries and strong exports"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 345260.0,
      "end_time": 349880.0,
      "text": "while others focus on services, tourism, or natural resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 349880.0,
      "end_time": 350970.0,
      "text": "On top of this, the"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 350970.0,
      "end_time": 353370.0,
      "text": "euro is the common currency of some but"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 353370.0,
      "end_time": 356500.0,
      "text": "not all of these countries."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 356500.0,
      "end_time": 361520.0,
      "text": "As the Greek crisis shows, this can be a recipe for disaster."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 361520.0,
      "end_time": 362880.0,
      "text": "You cannot unify a vastly"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 362880.0,
