      "text": "different economies under one currency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 364680.0,
      "end_time": 368460.0,
      "text": "but their economic policies separate."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 368460.0,
      "end_time": 370220.0,
      "text": "So, should all EU countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 370220.0,
