      "text": "unite under the common currency, or not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 373260.0,
      "end_time": 374700.0,
      "text": "Should the weakest links be thrown out"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 374700.0,
      "end_time": 377010.0,
      "text": "of the Euro, or should countries be made"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 377010.0,
      "end_time": 379650.0,
      "text": "to adopt common policies on taxes, health"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 379650.0,
      "end_time": 381880.0,
      "text": "care, and social security?"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 381880.0,
      "end_time": 384480.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a question that&#39;s been brewing for years, and is"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 384480.0,
      "end_time": 387540.0,
      "text": "nowhere near a solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 387540.0,
      "end_time": 390240.0,
      "text": "So, everything briefly considered: Is the"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 390240.0,
      "end_time": 392600.0,
      "text": "European Union worth it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 392600.0,
      "end_time": 394960.0,
      "text": "Here is our answer:"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 394960.0,
      "end_time": 397289.0,
      "text": "The EU is very flawed, and still"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 397289.0,
      "end_time": 399270.0,
      "text": "needs a lot of work. But it&#39;s fair to say"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 399270.0,
      "end_time": 403100.0,
      "text": "that the European Union makes Europeans powerful in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 403100.0,
      "end_time": 404099.0,
      "text": "Put together, we"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 404099.0,
      "end_time": 405690.0,
      "text": "lead in science, are one of the strongest"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 405690.0,
      "end_time": 408060.0,
      "text": "economic powers, and could have one of"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 408060.0,
      "end_time": 410500.0,
      "text": "the strongest militaries in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 410500.0,
      "end_time": 412560.0,
      "text": "But more importantly, the EU gives us"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 412560.0,
      "end_time": 416500.0,
      "text": "peace, security, and a sense of shared identity."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 416500.0,
      "end_time": 417960.0,
      "text": "And something we all crave"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 417960.0,
      "end_time": 421020.0,
      "text": "in these turbulent times, stability."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 421020.0,
      "end_time": 422849.0,
      "text": "If we want to protect the values we&#39;re so"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 422849.0,
      "end_time": 425070.0,
      "text": "proud of, a strong European Union is the"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 425070.0,
      "end_time": 427050.0,
      "text": "best way to make sure our voice is heard"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 427050.0,
      "end_time": 428800.0,
      "text": "in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 428800.0,
      "end_time": 430770.0,
      "text": "Alone as small states, we&#39;ll"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 430770.0,
      "end_time": 432780.0,
      "text": "hardly stand a chance in a world of"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 432780.0,
      "end_time": 437000.0,
      "text": "shifting superpowers."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 437000.0,
      "end_time": 439820.0,
      "text": "What do you think about the EU in its future?"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 439820.0,
      "end_time": 442320.0,
      "text": "In recent years, the discussion about political"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 442320.0,
      "end_time": 444620.0,
      "text": "topics has become super toxic with sad"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 444620.0,
      "end_time": 446560.0,
      "text": "real-world consequences."
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 446560.0,
      "end_time": 447980.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s not do that."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 447980.0,
      "end_time": 449160.0,
      "text": "If you don&#39;t agree with this video,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 449160.0,
      "end_time": 451320.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re not our enemy, you just have a"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 451320.0,
      "end_time": 453539.0,
      "text": "different opinion and that&#39;s fine."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 453539.0,
      "end_time": 455760.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re all in the same boat after all, so let&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 455760.0,
      "end_time": 465760.0,
      "text": "have a fact-based discussion about our future."
    }
